      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to me. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape, super reliable, and drives like a dream! The interior is nice and clean, and it's clearly been well-loved over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels great on the road. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re gonna love it!",
