    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, having undergone proactive rear subframe reinforcement and a recent refresh of the rear trailing arm bushings (RTABs). The double VANOS system operates smoothly without noise, and the cooling system has been overhauled with a high-flow water pump. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the car exhibits minor stone chips and light interior patina consistent with its age, but remains mechanically robust with linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A purist-spec M-car ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
