    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a reliable daily driver that strikes a perfect balance between performance and comfort. The exterior paint still holds a brilliant, deep shine, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and strictly non-smoker; the premium leather upholstery is in great shape, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control and heated seats to the premium infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is very sound\u2014the engine starts instantly and runs quietly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains firm yet comfortable without any unusual noises. It recently passed a full safety inspection, received a fresh synthetic oil change, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. Included with the sale are two sets of keys, the original owner's manuals, and a folder of recent service records. This is a solid, honest car that has been well-loved and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
