      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my trips. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today! If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels great, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
