    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s build featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a functional M-variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement and upgraded polyurethane bushings for enhanced torsional rigidity. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and cooling system overhaul, ensuring the mechanical vitals remain within factory tolerances. A well-sorted performance icon that balances analog feedback with razor-sharp handling.",
